thread.title: TV | TFI Friday

author: Fiona Flynn
title: TV | TFI Friday
text: Second episode in this new series of TFI Friday making its welcome return to Friday nights after the success of the 25th anniversary edition over the summer. So far so good too, Chris Evans has managed to recreate the live off-the-cuff feel of the original series with yet another fantastic lineup of guests tonight. Joining him will be Justin Bieber, actress Dawn French, hip hop stars Macklemore & Ryan Lewis, X-Men: Apocalypse actor Nicholas Hoult and synthpop duo Hurts. Don't miss it.
